deb_postinst
  Creates a backup of the blacklist-netronome.conf file
  Registers the autorun script with rc.d
  Enables autorun with rc.d
  Clear any old CoreNIC config on the system
  Generates inital CoreNIC config for the system

deb_prerm
  Clear any existing CoreNIC config on the system
  Restores backup of blacklist-netronome.conf
  Disables autorun with rc.d

deb_postrm
  Removes registration with rc.d

ns-vrouter-core-nic.autorun
  /etc/init.d script that is registerd rc.d

ns-vrouter-core-nic-setup
  Logs to system 'logger' and to /opt/netronome/log
  This is the main helper script used to configure CoreNIC
  This script modifies udev rules to name devices nfp_pX
  This script modifies blacklist-netronome.conf to allow nfp_net to load first
  This script moves the nic.cat firmware to /lib/firmware/netronome/nfp6000_net.cat
    for the appropriate platform
    PLATFORMS
      - 1x40G Hydrogen
      - 4x10G Hydrogen (Breakout cable)
      - 2x10G Lithium
      - 2x40G Beryllium

